thing again.","dimension":5,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.014276,0.04317,0.06692,0.082238,0.090247,0.096339,0.098866,0.10364,0.10832,0.11192,0.10413,0.079933],"unified_progress":[0.030072,0.058777,0.07096,0.084618,0.087224,0.090124,0.094632,0.096084,0.097232,0.10322,0.097677,0.089385]},{"section":27,"text":"Respiratory problems, allergies, eosinophilia - it really does seem like Loeffler's syndrome is a strong contender here.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.019446,0.039133,0.050962,0.061027,0.068956,0.077177,0.085515,0.090779,0.099532,0.11383,0.14318,0.15046],"unified_progress":[0.025991,0.04565,0.058366,0.06697,0.076066,0.085062,0.088856,0.095471,0.10229,0.10754,0.11927,0.12847]},{"section":28,"text":"But wait, let's not forget about asthma.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.010842,0.028549,0.045192,0.058731,0.072347,0.090045,0.10911,0.13244,0.1498,0.15124,0.10639,0.045313],"unified_progress":[0.023935,0.049916,0.065053,0.07531,0.086939,0.091494,0.099306,0.10803,0.11033,0.12298,0.10226,0.064449]},{"section":29,"text":"It's common in kids and can definitely cause wheezing and respiratory distress.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.020383,0.028891,0.036351,0.0448,0.055933,0.069655,0.086801,0.10123,0.11837,0.14202,0.16512,0.13044],"unified_progress":[0.032785,0.047188,0.05929,0.069423,0.081133,0.093333,0.09739,0.10474,0.10885,0.1113,0.10776,0.086796]},{"section":30,"text":"Hmm, I'm leaning towards asthma as the main issue here.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.015311,0.030755,0.041803,0.051575,0.060405,0.070813,0.081959,0.093389,0.1072,0.12237,0.15458,0.16983],"unified_progress":[0.021634,0.040911,0.05201,0.061548,0.069338,0.081071,0.085646,0.09826,0.10597,0.11299,0.1279,0.14272]},{"section":31,"text":"The respiratory alkalosis and wheezing fit well with asthma.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"mode